%h1 Downloadable data files

%p
  These data files are generated daily from the subset of our data that has been
  reviewed. If a file is unavailable, the text in question has not yet been reviewed or the file is in the process of being (re)generated.

%p
  All data files are released under the
  != link_to "CC BY-NC-SA 3.0", "http://creativecommons.org/licenses/by-nc-sa/3.0/us/"
  license. Please make sure that you are familiar with the terms of this license before downloading any of the files below.

%h2 Data files

%table
  - Source.all.each do |s|
    %tr
      %td!= link_to s.author_and_title, s
      - Proiel::export_formats.each do |name, format|
        %td!= link_to_if Proiel::export_file_available?(s.human_readable_id, format), name, Proiel::export_file_url(s.human_readable_id, format)

